<h1>CDN Build</h1>

<p>
  The standard grigson bundle embeds all font subsets as base64 data URIs, so charts render
  with no network requests. This makes it easy to drop into any page with a single
  <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> tag, but the file is around 270 KB.
</p>
<p>
  A CDN build is also available, where the font files are fetched on demand from
  <a href="https://www.jsdelivr.com/?docs=gh">jsDelivr</a> rather than bundled inline.
  This brings the script down to around 75 KB, at the cost of a network dependency for fonts.
</p>

<h2>Usage</h2>

<p>
  Swap <code>grigson-register.iife.js</code> for <code>grigson-cdn-register.iife.js</code>.
  Everything else — the <code>&lt;grigson-chart&gt;</code> element, attributes, CSS custom
  properties — is identical.
</p>

<pre><code>&lt;!-- Standard build (~270 KB, fonts embedded) -->
&lt;script src="grigson-register.iife.js">&lt;/script>

&lt;!-- CDN build (~75 KB, fonts from jsDelivr) -->
&lt;script src="grigson-cdn-register.iife.js">&lt;/script>

&lt;!-- Usage is the same either way -->
&lt;grigson-chart normalise>
  &lt;template>
    | Cm7 | F7 | BbMaj7 | Ebmaj7 |
    | Am7b5 | D7 | Gm | % |
  &lt;/template>
&lt;/grigson-chart></code></pre>

<h2>Content Security Policy</h2>

<p>
  Because the CDN build fetches font files from <code>cdn.jsdelivr.net</code>, your page's
  Content Security Policy must allow it:
</p>

<pre><code>Content-Security-Policy: font-src 'self' cdn.jsdelivr.net;</code></pre>

<p>
  No other CSP changes are needed — the JavaScript itself is still served from your own host.
</p>

<h2>Live demo</h2>

<p>
  The chart below is rendered by the CDN build. Open the Network panel in your browser's
  devtools and you should see the WOFF2 font files being fetched from
  <code>cdn.jsdelivr.net</code>.
</p>

<iframe id="cdn-demo" class="cdn-demo" title="CDN build demo"></iframe>

<script>
  const chart = `---
title: "Autumn Leaves"
key: G minor
meter: 4/4
---

[A]
||: Cm7 | F7 | BbMaj7 | EbMaj7 |
| Am7b5 | D7 | Gm | % :|

[B]
| Am7b5 | D7 | Gm | % |
| Cm7 | F7 | BbMaj7 | % |
| Am7b5 | D7 | Gm | D7 ||`;

  const srcdoc = `<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      body { margin: 1rem; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; }
    </style>
    <script src="/js/grigson-cdn-register.iife.js"><\/script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <grigson-chart normalise>
      <template>${chart}<\/template>
    </grigson-chart>
  </body>
</html>`;

  const frame = document.getElementById('cdn-demo');
  frame.srcdoc = srcdoc;
  frame.addEventListener('load', () => {
    frame.style.height = frame.contentDocument.body.scrollHeight + 32 + 'px';
  });
</script>

